title: The Dutch World of Painting (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
The Dutch World of Painting
Vancouver Art Gallery | 1986 | ISBN: 9061790646 | English | 170 pages | PDF | 20.3 MB

The catalogue of an exhibition of one hundred Dutch paintings held in the Vancouver Art Gallery from April 6 to June 29, 1986. Organized by the Netherlands Office for Fine Arts (Rijksdienst Beeldende Kunst). The Dutch world of painting seen against the fascinating background of the society of which it was an integral part. The fully illustrated catalogue is divided into nine sections
